! Formatting using CSS 
Format the results using html and css. Here an ordered list is used followed with an ordered list format.

```
<style>
 .myClass {
 color:red;
 font-size:1.1em;
 
 }
</style>

<ul class="myClass">
<$list filter="[[Tiddler-A]] [[Tiddler-B]] [[Tiddler-C]]">
<li><<currentTiddler>></li>
</$list>
</ul>
```

